description:
Check out the awesome new look of the AddictingGames App! While you're at it, see if you can beat our latest game: Zomboffice! Race Zombies to the Exit!

Put a bunch of AddictingGames in your pocket. One FREE download delivers tons of ridiculously fun games straight to your device. For the first time on mobile, get online hits like Man-Eating Castle, Zombie Burger, and 50+ other great games from the AddictingGames catalog.

Hundreds of levels, 300+ achievements to unlock, hours of fun – and more games coming at you all the time! One single download brings you an epic game experience.

What’s in it? Perfect Hoopz 2, Release the Mooks, Break Monsters Out, Addictive Balance, Escape the Car and more!

Plus, brand new mobile games you will not find anywhere else - like Potty Copter, the latest craptacular adventure from the people who brought you Potty Racers!

Compare your high scores against your Facebook friends and all other AddictingGames mobile players with our recently added Global Leaderboards! Share your best scores on Facebook and Twitter! Unlock dozens of crazy achievements!

Did we mention it’s completely free?

Stop playing crap games on the bus; start playing bio-fueled poo-tastic games from AddictingGames NOW and join millions of peeps already playing AddictingGames on Facebook and addictinggames.com.
